org.pircbotx.hooks

Class TemporaryListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pircbotx.hooks.ListenerAdapter
      • org.pircbotx.hooks.TemporaryListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Listener

    public class TemporaryListener
extends ListenerAdapter
    Listener for short one-off tasks. Listener methods will only be called if the event matches the specified bot. Listener can easily be removed with done().

    Author:
    Leon Blakey
